descriptionHtml:
----------------
Riverwood players house (ver1.0)
----------------

This is a house of a player. 
It is very poor. 

[color=green]This is MOD for those who are suffering troubles in the early stage of a game.[/color]

[color=red]Please be sure to back up your save data.[/color]


---
Author : hdela


---
This mod was built with Skyrim US Ver.


---
Installation : Unzip the file, and drop the data folder into your Skyrim Data directory. 


---
Location : The house is located in the crow\'s-nest of Riverwood.


---
v1.0 : First MOD

Single bed x2, No respawn container x7, etc.


---
Enjoy!

by hdela
author: hdela
